It's now deserted

4
01:00:44.200 --> 01:00:45.928 
兰若寺后面是乱葬岗
Behind it is the grave

5
01:00:48.233 --> 01:00:49.358 
乱葬岗？
Grave?

6
01:00:52.467 --> 01:00:54.160 
这几年来，时局不定
Because of the chaotic situation

7
